HEADWORD: Cowbane
<hw>Cow"bane`</hw> <pr>(kou"b⟦amac⟧n`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A poisonous umbelliferous plant; in England, the
<spn>Cicuta virosa</spn>; in the United States, the <spn>Cicuta
maculata</spn> and the <spn>Archemora rigida</spn>. See <er>Water
hemlock</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cowberry</ent>⟦br⟧
